reviewText:
Brothers - A Tale of Two Sons: it not a game. Its a piece of art, an adventure that is able to stir with all your feelings.

.Unique and solid gameplay if you have a JPAD;
.A wonderful story told in a unique and spectacular way;

This game bring back my older brother to life.
altough he is cool, he made one wrong decission that brought him to his death.

for my brother, rest in peace :'-(
